name: Thaydjowa
description:
Guerreiros! Meu povo fala que na nossa cultura os guerreiros descem das estrelas com a energia da natureza, dos animais, das águas e do fogo. Na nossa aldeia os anciãos são donos das histórias, os guerreiros da aldeia e as crianças do mundo. 🏹🏹🏹
---
Warriors! My people say that in our culture, warriors descend from the stars with the energy of nature, animals, water and fire. In our village, the elders are the owners of the stories, the warriors of the village and the children of the world.
